<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="cn"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.4.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://nuts-btc.github.io/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://nuts-btc.github.io/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="cn"/><updated>2025-04-26T07:06:49+00:00</updated><id>https://nuts-btc.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">blank</title><subtitle>Nuts坚果Blog,技术分析博主,币安合约交易大赛斩获100Wu+，纯实盘公开策略 </subtitle><entry><title type="html">学会维加斯通道，做BNB犹如送钱</title><link href="https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/Vegas-BNB/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="学会维加斯通道，做BNB犹如送钱"/><published>2025-04-26T04:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-04-26T04:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/Vegas-BNB</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/Vegas-BNB/"><![CDATA[<p>维加斯通道的设置，以及各种资金体量下BNB的布局和止盈方案</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Lk1eDkUPn4" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen="" width="auto" height="auto"/> </figure> </div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="Binance"/><category term="BNB"/><category term="Vegas"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[学会维加斯通道，做BNB犹如送钱]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">常见问题解答</title><link href="https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/FAQ/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="常见问题解答"/><published>2025-04-20T15:59:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-04-20T15:59:00+00:00</updated><id>https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/FAQ</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/FAQ/"><![CDATA[<h1 id="看盘软件推荐">看盘软件推荐</h1> <p><a href="https://www.tradingview.com/">TradingView</a>，全世界优秀交易员都在用的看盘软件，付费ess会员就够用了</p> <h1 id="如何设置维加斯通道">如何设置【维加斯通道】</h1> <p>在 TradingView 的指标中搜索<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pulu</code>，选择<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Pulu's Moving Averages</code>即可</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/FAQ/01-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/FAQ/01-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/FAQ/01-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/FAQ/01.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>在之后就可以在界面中看到三条通道线</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/FAQ/02-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/FAQ/02-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/FAQ/02-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/FAQ/02.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>第一条默认是12，离K线太近，不容易分辨，可以将其更改为21</p> <div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>短周期均线组21/55
快轨144/169
中轨288/338
慢轨576/676
</code></pre></div></div> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/FAQ/03-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/FAQ/03-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/FAQ/03-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/FAQ/03.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>操作视频</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Lk1eDkUPn4&amp;t=180s" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen="" width="auto" height="auto"/> </figure> </div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="Binance"/><category term="TradingView"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[常见问题解答]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">币安注册及绑定返佣</title><link href="https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/Register-Binance/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="币安注册及绑定返佣"/><published>2025-04-20T15:59:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-04-20T15:59:00+00:00</updated><id>https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/Register-Binance</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://nuts-btc.github.io/blog/2025/Register-Binance/"><![CDATA[<h1 id="新用户">新用户</h1> <h2 id="电脑版">电脑版</h2> <p>点击访问注册链接 <a href="https://accounts.binance.com/zh-CN/register?ref=MQ01QU2G">注册币安</a></p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/01-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/01-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/01-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/01.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>输入验证码后，设置密码信息</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/02-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/02-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/02-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/02.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>使用上面的注册链接默认直接填写了返佣邀请码，如果没有默认选用，请选择有邀请人，并填入邀请码 <strong>MQ01QU2G</strong></p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/03-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/03-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/03-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/03.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>之后进行KYC认证即可</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/04-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/04-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/04-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/04.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <h2 id="手机版">手机版</h2> <p>选择注册/登录</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/05-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/05-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/05-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/05.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>按照流程进行注册</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/06-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/06-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/06-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/06.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>接收验证码以后，输入密码</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/07-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/07-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/07-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/07.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>请选择有邀请人，并填入邀请码 <strong>MQ01QU2G</strong></p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/08-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/08-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/08-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/08.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <p>之后进行KYC认证即可</p> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/Register-Binance/09-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/09-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/Register-Binance/09-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/Register-Binance/09.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> <h1 id="老用户">老用户</h1> <p>半年没有进行交易的老用户，是可以直接进行绑定的，除此之外，请重新注册并按照上述流程进行注册</p> <h2 id="方案一解绑身份认证">方案一:解绑身份认证</h2> <p>如果需要使用同一个用户身份进行认证，请先解绑当前的身份认证。</p> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <video src="/assets/video/Binance-UnbindingKYC.mp4" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="auto" height="auto" autoplay="" controls=""/> </figure> </div> </div> <h2 id="方案二注销账户">方案二:注销账户</h2> <p>如果选择注销账户，重新注册，请使用护照进行，认证可以秒过</p> <p>如果仍使用身份证进行认证，请等待五天后，再进行认证。</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="Binance"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[币安注册及绑定返佣]]></summary></entry></feed>